\nbandwidth. Based on all these results, we propose a quantum phase transition\nfrom a paramagnetic Anderson insulating state to a ferromagnetic MBL insulating\nphase via an intermediate ferromagnetic metallic state, which intervenes\nbetween these two insulators at the Fermi energy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Jul 2022 03:28:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-12"}
