$\\kappa/g \\approx 0.71\\%$) to\nencode a logical qubit with the error rate $2.53\\times10^{-7}$, compared with\nthe qubit-based surface code using 3041 qubits to achieve almost the same\nlogical error rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Jul 2022 04:50:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Oct 2022 07:31:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 10 Apr 2023 08:07:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-11"}
